{"tid":330445,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我的媽呀】全運會項目增設大媽廣場舞","createTime":"2017-07-21T08:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T08:35:59.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0bcc92ac4b16b81c0d1f15c5011946bf596d5d02","tid":330445,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T08:21:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170721&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56982562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170721%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56982562&d=n7P4D0%2BhRwhYbBmgpuBG%2BOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=cb60d148\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170721%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D56982562&h=22e90b71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170721&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=56982562</a><br />\n【我的媽呀】全運會項目增設大媽廣場舞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大媽舞都變運動項目？唔係同你講笑，呢隻所謂嘅廣場舞，已被列入第13屆中國全運會比賽項目中。<br />\n<br />\n據《中國新聞網》記者由「我要上全運」全民健身網絡競賽活動的新聞發佈會上，得悉呢個消息，仲話廣場舞係舞蹈藝術中最龐大嘅系統，呢種因在廣場聚集而得名、將自娛同表演融為一體嘅舞蹈，已經逐漸成為最受民眾歡迎嘅一種休閑娛樂健身活動，現在被納入比賽項目，證明官方對呢種舞蹈嘅肯定。<br />\n<br />\n報道又話50多年歷史嘅全運會，近年隨住國家體育改革，功能同價值觀一直改變緊，希望可以有多元發掘及展現，增設更多群眾可以參與嘅項目，好似今年就19個項目開設群眾性嘅比賽，包括馬拉松、羽毛球、國際跳棋及乒乓球等，而大媽舞亦喺呢種背景下應運而生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那柒夠未"},{"pid":"bd1f21de79ad22155010580aec50160060fd7d0f","tid":330445,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T08:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2630ac7948e06ce03b1d770f840ad37b1bcd7636","tid":330445,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 